twcore.bots.multibot.killer
Class killer

java.lang.Object
  twcore.bots.MultiModule
      twcore.bots.multibot.killer.killer

public class killer
extends MultiModule

TWBot Extension for use in any arena, particularly deathmatch. One person is the killer, and all of their shots spec without message. If a person guesses who they are, they become the killer, but guess wrong and they are spec'd. When there are two people left, it becomes a showdown, with the next hit spec'ing. Other than that, a normal elim. Last person standing wins.

Version:
1.9
Author:
qan
